{"tid":996980,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"人地都係打份工啫⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-01-26T17:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T17:49:04.000Z","uid":125898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f38a84dcfa9c673e6e9ff8d820d0264a85eb8184","tid":996980,"uid":125898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T17:49:04.000Z","msg":"有時候面對嘅困難都可能係一個出口<br />\n<br />\nRebecca Saha 有3個仔女<br />\n屋企有好多玩具<br />\n玩完一陣就唔要真係好浪費<br />\n所以佢就決定搵方法改善<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/27/014000_ccfc6c45eb75c0e7ec2d8836f623d956.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F014000_ccfc6c45eb75c0e7ec2d8836f623d956.png&h=ed24f679&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/27/014001_128769892ac3fc3ed9210f81d7f28cc1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F014001_128769892ac3fc3ed9210f81d7f28cc1.png&h=2ca1edc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRebecca本身係小學教師，教左18年<br />\n佢自己認為玩呢，對小朋友黎講係世界級<br />\n因為玩係小朋友同呢個世界接觸既一個好好既媒界<br />\n不單只能夠幫助建構小朋友腦部既發展成長<br />\n亦能夠帶領小朋友有效地同其他人結交<br />\n有助人際關係<br />\n<br />\n所以佢將本身已經無用既舊玩具變成教學工具<br />\n例如可以將D Marker 蓋，提升轉型<br />\n變成識字同數學遊戲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/27/014034_c7b5e61ff5683fd903f4de84c5035505.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F014034_c7b5e61ff5683fd903f4de84c5035505.png&h=603abe36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/27/014035_f37d68e1e5cd87b0e415847dd8b21c41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F014035_f37d68e1e5cd87b0e415847dd8b21c41.png&h=0833010d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/27/014143_bfb6f3a9615978aff65d8ff69322b541.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F014143_bfb6f3a9615978aff65d8ff69322b541.png&h=904d54de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/27/014145_f0eecd0209033a5112e217a8c38ce5ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F014145_f0eecd0209033a5112e217a8c38ce5ec.png&h=c76225c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/27/014147_ae996e6c6d97274ebe395a178014db51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F014147_ae996e6c6d97274ebe395a178014db51.png&h=a6cb64ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家更成立左一間Tiny Toy Co既公司<br />\n公開收集公眾唔要既玩具<br />\n引起社會好大迴響<br />\n亦都吸引咗大群老師們、語言病理學家<br />\n環保人士既注意<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/27/014210_69fed39a23812401356d78262bd46441.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F014210_69fed39a23812401356d78262bd46441.png&h=9759c522&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/27/014211_f5e66bd833312689640f7a93d62f2044.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F014211_f5e66bd833312689640f7a93d62f2044.png&h=ee7187ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFrom: CBC news<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/how-one-toronto-woman-is-turning-unwanted-toy-debris-into-new-learning-experiences-1.4984425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Ftoronto%2Fhow-one-toronto-woman-is-turning-unwanted-toy-debris-into-new-learning-experiences-1.4984425&d=Ew3NtGOXJSp836VkgkjnQNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d0710606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/how-one-toronto-woman-is-turning-unwanted-toy-debris-into-new-learning-experiences-1.4984425</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/5823419603/posts/10157240015484604/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F5823419603%2Fposts%2F10157240015484604%2F&d=Ew3NtGOXJSp836VkgkjnQNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4bf65814\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/5823419603/posts/10157240015484604/</a>"}]}